        .card
          .row
            .col-sm-3
              img src="/images/kevin.jpg"
                      
            .col-sm-9
              h3 Kevin McGillivray
              p.meta Instructor, Web Developer, Curriculum Developer
                  
              p Hay, I'm Kevin! I'm a teacher, designer, and web developer. I've been working as a web developer for the past three years, and have been enamored with all things technology and web since I was very young. I love building websites because I love to contribute to this huge resource of knowledge and awesome things we call the Internet, and I can't get enough of learning about how it works and sharing what I learn with others. More than anything I love learning about and practicing creativity and sharing what I learn through teaching, writing, and other projects. I like books, games, tea, mindfulness, and trying to figure out how creativity works. My favorite word is “studio.”
          
