        h2 Frequently asked questions
        
        .row
          .col-md-6
            h3 Do I need to have prior experience?
            p No prior experience is necessary – the course is designed to meet the learning needs of all students from complete beginner to advanced.
            
          .col-md-6              
            h3 What are the age requirements?
            p The course is open to all students ages 12 and up.
        
        .row
          .col-md-6
            h3 Do I need a laptop?
            p A laptop is required. We're working to develop more resources for students without a laptop, but a laptop is essential for practice in and out of the classroom.
          
          .col-md-6          
            h3 What are the technical requirements?
            p The course is mainly Mac and OSX based, but we can accomodate Windows systems as well.

